{"tid":147150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【的士不顧而去】婚禮攝影師好轉︰我冇事 多謝大家關心","createTime":"2017-03-07T15:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T14:33:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8eebb9117b2b9e6da51e562d365c25b20b8bb0","tid":147150,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"婚禮攝影師Solo昨晚遭的士撞傷，司機事後不顧而去，至今日被警方尋獲。Solo左手骨折及頭部受傷，一度需要留醫伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部，至今晚8時許，Solo情況終於好轉，轉往普通病房繼續留醫觀察。<br />\n<br />\nSolo戴上口罩、一臉倦容躺在病床上由護士推往普通病房，其間向記者稱只是「皮外傷」，並表示「我冇事，多謝大家關心」，Solo又指暫時記不起車禍的經過，「被人撞前後1個鐘都唔記得」。被問及會否譴責涉事司機時，他笑指「我連佢係邊個都唔知，冇晒記憶」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170307/large/1488890841_7e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F1488890841_7e0d.jpg&h=f90e26cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Solo情況終於好轉，轉往普通病房繼續留醫觀察。(徐雲庭攝)</span>"},{"pid":"179ac4de547c6ff19fd06c79a43f0c90a857d8c7","tid":147150,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAG8088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAG8088.jpg&h=928c9b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8fa2964e502bcca8ab239e2b58e92eb6f0701d","tid":147150,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAG8088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAG8088.jpg&h=928c9b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴正執法"},{"pid":"bf3e77305dbe59275500e233a09900d911b2d621","tid":147150,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"而家d hit&amp;Run case 猶太人係咪唔會再理